ygData.messageBody:
The keys go to the slaves, if you give the right key to the right slave, you
get experience.

Since the slaves aren't numbered like the keys, you have to get creative.
The trick to this is to give each slave 1 copper piece, and the slave will
tell you which key they need.

Wenaddar
